-- IVRCL Assets Plans 6-Billion Rupee Share Sale for Expansion, Times Reports
-- B y   T h o m a s   A b r a h a m
-- 2010-11-10T00:55:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/ivrcl-assets-plans-6-billion-rupee-share-sale-for-expansion-times-reports.html
 IVRCL Assets & Holdings Ltd. plans
to raise 6 billion rupees ($135 million) selling shares to large
investors to finance expansion, the Economic Times reported,
citing S. Ramachandran, a company director. The company may sell
as much as a 49 percent stake in three of its road projects, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
